  "description": "This individual is a broad-shouldered human of early middle years, built for sustained watch duty and close-quarters restraint. Brown eyes sit beneath a heavy brow, and brown hair is kept in a short, regulation cut that exposes a squared jawline. Bronze skin bears old knuckle-thickened calluses and a faint, healed split at the lower lip consistent with repeated blows. The overall physiognomy reads as disciplined and unadorned, shaped by routine drill rather than ornamentation.",
